reviewText: It was wonderful! The seller sent it to me immediately and it is in really good shape.  It is a priceless thing to own. Worth the money. Is a diamond in my collection of Cagney memorabilia. So grateful to have it.

This film is so good that Two people have borrowed it from me and I had to chase them to get it returned.  It shows cagney at his best and shows off some of hollywood royalty like sinatra, Reagan, Blondel, Wayne and Eastwood.  A must see.
